WEBVTT

00:01:28.958 --> 00:01:30.998
u 3:30 popodne, zbili bismo se

00:01:30.998 --> 00:01:34.248
pokraj TV-a, i poput obijača sefova,

00:01:34.248 --> 00:01:36.734
vrteli bismo dugme za jačinu tona

00:01:36.734 --> 00:01:39.527
na TV-u tako da bude skoro nečujan.

00:01:39.527 --> 00:01:41.838
I ponekad, kad smo bili takvi,

00:01:41.838 --> 00:01:44.270
toliko se puta "Pssst"

00:01:44.270 --> 00:01:46.135
čulo po kući

00:01:46.135 --> 00:01:48.110
da sam zamišljao da smo kao

00:01:48.110 --> 00:01:51.610
nemačka posada u podmornici

00:01:51.610 --> 00:01:54.102
koja se šunja duž ivice okeana

00:01:54.102 --> 00:01:55.918
dok gore, na površini,

00:01:55.918 --> 00:01:59.663
patrolira brod HMS Podočnjak

00:01:59.663 --> 00:02:01.790
spreman da donese smrtnu presudu